<p>I'm developing an android screen lock app. Lock screen Activity works fine and it has one custom ImageView control . This control was extended from ImageView Control. When touch event raised , a circle will be draw in control.This control works fine in another Activity but in my LockScreen activity it fails to draw circle. I use debuger and it shows that touch event is capture but the code that draw circle , do not effect. Code is shown below :<br> Custom image view :  </p>  <pre><code>@Override  protected void onDraw(Canvas canvas) {     super.onDraw(canvas);     //canvas.drawPath(path, drawPaint);     //canvas.drawCircle(50,50,5,drawPaint);     for(int i=0;i&lt;points.size();i++)     {         canvas.drawCircle(points.get(i)[0], points.get(i)[1], (float) DistanceThreshold/2, drawPaint);     }  }  // Append new circle each time user presses on screen @Override public boolean onTouchEvent(MotionEvent event) {     float[] point = {event.getX(),event.getY()};     boolean isNewPoint = true;     for(int i=0;i&lt;points.size();i++)     {         if(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(event.getX()-points.get(i)[0], 2)+Math.pow(event.getY()-points.get(i)[1], 2))&lt;=                 DistanceThreshold)         {             isNewPoint = false;             break;         }     }     if(isNewPoint)      {         points.add(point);      }      postInvalidate();      return true; }   </code></pre>  <p>And Lock Screen Activity :  </p>  <pre><code>     @Override public void onAttachedToWindow() {      this.getWindow().setType(             WindowManager.LayoutParams.TYPE_KEYGUARD_DIALOG);     this.getWindow().addFlags(             WindowManager.LayoutParams.FLAG_FULLSCREEN                     | WindowManager.LayoutParams.FLAG_SHOW_WHEN_LOCKED                     | WindowManager.LayoutParams.FLAG_KEEP_SCREEN_ON                     | WindowManager.LayoutParams.FLAG_DISMISS_KEYGUARD                     );           super.onAttachedToWindow();   } </code></pre>  <p>I really have no idea what is wrong.<br>  Tank's for your help and your attention. </p>